    {
      "review_id": "rkxBU7f0qH",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "text": "- the authors state that they use \"the power of DNNs\" while they are experimenting with a neural network with only 4 layers. While there is no clear line between shallow and deep neural networks, I would argue that a 4 layer NN is rather shallow.",
