      "coarse": "arg_evaluative",
      "fine": "none",
      "asp": "asp_substance",
      "pol": "pol_negative"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rkxBU7f0qH",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "text": "- the authors fix the number of layers of the used network based on \"our experience\". For the sake of completeness, more experiments in this area would be nice.",
